Reese & Chris’s party in the USA 🇺🇸 such an incredible day celebrating them! Thanks to all of our friends & family for coming out & to everyone else that came out to make this party everything is was!! @asliceofnewjersey @paulyblues @flowers.by.lisa.ny
Let freedom ring 🇺🇸 such a fun 4th of July spent with friends!

Yesterday Reese turned 2. She is the definition of sugar & spice . She’s silly, sassy and so cuddly . She is filled with so much love!!! She will always express how she’s feeling even if she’s not happy about something . She holds her own with her brother & isn’t scared to put him in his place! She keeps us all on our toes & everyday is such an adventure with her. Our little baby 💕💕💕

So thankful !!!!! My crew ❤️❤️❤️ happy thanksgiving to all !

We traveled from New York to Indio, CA where Cameron got to compete with @bbl_boys at the @sandstormlacrosse tournament - he played against teams from Texas, California & Colorado . It was an incredible experience! So proud of my boy who works so hard at this sport & proud of this team!! They made it to the semi finals - Big things ahead for 2024 !!! This is just the beginning 🥍
#proudmom - all the time he spends practicing & dedicating to this sport shows!! Big things to come for cam!! @cam01_lax ❤️🥍 #laxmom
